## Updating Documents
curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/customer/external/1/_update?pretty' -d '
{
  "doc": { "name": "Jane Doe" }
}'

## update our previous document
curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/customer/external/1/_update?pretty' -d '
{
  "doc": { "name": "Jane Doe", "age": 20 }
}'

##未测试成功
curl -XPOST 'localhost:9200/customer/external/1/_update?pretty' -d '
{
  "script" : "ctx._source.age += 5"
}'